    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i thought natural stuff works better with the body? my friend told me that if you just keep your vitamin k levels high and steady, it basically does the same thing as the medicine without all the side effects. and garlic is a natural blood thinner anyway. isn't there a way to just dose the supplements and the smoothies to keep everything balanced so i can skip the warfarin?",
